4
00:00:15,360 --> 00:00:17,950
So, what are you going to do?

5
00:00:17,950 --> 00:00:21,250
Well, you rely on their innate capacities.

6
00:00:21,250 --> 00:00:22,580
We know they’ve got reflexes.

7
00:00:22,580 --> 00:00:28,040
So, maybe we can make use of the fact that they can suck, and they can grasp.

8
