distance.

11
00:00:36,980 --> 00:00:42,190
We can also make use of habituation, which is just a characteristic of all living things.

12
00:00:42,190 --> 00:00:47,900
Repeated stimulation of the same form becomes less potent over time; it’s just boredom.

13
